NUMBER 2355
NAME River Hawk, Captain Dark's Cabin
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT 
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
The cabin has two windows forward and windowed doors to either side. The base
of the Topmast stands in the center of the cabin. Hanging from a hook on the
Topmast is a mesh bag full of fresh fruits and vegetables. A large bed sits
under the two forward windows. A pair of trunks are used for storage. The after
bulkhead of the cabin is painted with a realistic mural of a marsh.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;------port door--------
