NAME River Hawk, Bridge Deck
DAY_LIGHT 
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
This flat area aft of the bridge is called the "Dryout." It is used to dry
ropes and canvas, It is also sometimes used for sunbathing by the crew when
