NUMBER 2364
NAME River Hawk, Bridge
DAY_LIGHT 
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is the highest compartment on the River Hawk, and the place with the best
visibility. It is surrounded with windows, with a windowed door in the after
bulkhead. The Captain steers the River Hawk from here, using a large, spoked
Wooden wheel.
*DESCRIPTION_END
